    <SupplProvision AmendLawId="407261" AmendLawNum="平成七年六月二六日政令第二六一号" Extract="false" Id="b5fe64ca-7f1c-4d57-bfab-852d1e139d78" Type="Amend">
      <SupplProvisionLabel>附　則</SupplProvisionLabel>
      <Paragraph Hide="false" Num="1" OldStyle="false">
